#EXTINF:-1 tvg-logo="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w600_and_h900_bestv2/i0sNYuHQmRkmin2dUapIYce7W2y.jpg" group-title="|IT| DRAMMATICO/ROMATICO" tvg-type="movie" description="A boy escaped from home, listening, crouched in the depths of his hiding place, the cries of the men who seek him. When the game passes, what remains before him is an infinite and arid plain that he must cross if he wants to get away definitively from what has made him flee. His steps will intersect with those of a pastor and, from that moment, nothing will be the same for either of them." year="2019-11-22" director="Benito Zambrano" actors="Luis Tosar, Luis Callejo, Vicente Romero Sánchez, Kandido Uranga, Mona Martínez, Adriano Carvalho, María Alfonsa Rosso, Yoima Valdés, Manolo Caro, Carlos Cabra",IT - Out in the Open (2019)
